Originally Answered: Which mobile phone should I buy? ·

My answer is going to be in a Commerce perspective. Making an investment on a Mobile phone is a dead investment. So, think before you buy a phone. Make a list of pros and cons of the mobile phones which you like.

If you are rich then you can buy any phone on this planet. You can go for iPhone 11 or the Samsung S10 or the One Plus 7T, etc. If you are on a budget, then Google for some of the budget smartphones. You might find some great phones from MI, Oppo, Vivo, Samsung, etc.

I particularly like Poco F1, since its a budget phone, with almost the same features of OnePlus 5 and 6 series.
